org.supremica.automata
Class LabelTrace

java.lang.Object
  org.supremica.automata.LabelTrace

public class LabelTrace
extends java.lang.Object

Models an event trace. Instead of storing the event we do store only the label. This is done because we might want to use the same trace in several automata. Since the events is different for different automata we do only store the labels.
